params.name: id
params.description: Event id.

params.name: calendarId
params.description: Calendar id.

params.name: title
params.description: Event title.

params.name: body
params.description: Body content of the event.

params.name: isAllday
params.description: Whether the event is all day or not.

params.name: start
params.description: Start time of the event.

params.name: end
params.description: End time of the event.

params.name: goingDuration
params.description: Travel time which is taken to go in minutes.

params.name: comingDuration
params.description: Travel time which is taken to come back in minutes.

params.name: location
params.description: Location of the event.

params.name: attendees
params.description: Attendees of the event.

params.name: category
params.description: Category of the event. Available categories are 'milestone', 'task', 'time' and 'allday'.

params.name: dueDateClass
params.description: Classification of work events. (before work, before lunch, before work)

params.name: recurrenceRule
params.description: Recurrence rule of the event.

params.name: state
params.description: State of the event. Available states are 'Busy', 'Free'.

params.name: isVisible
params.description: Whether the event is visible or not.

params.name: isPending
params.description: Whether the event is pending or not.

params.name: isFocused
params.description: Whether the event is focused or not.

params.name: isReadOnly
params.description: Whether the event is read only or not.

params.name: isPrivate
params.description: Whether the event is private or not.

params.name: color
params.description: Text color of the event.

params.name: backgroundColor
params.description: Background color of the event.

params.name: dragBackgroundColor
params.description: Background color of the event during dragging.

params.name: borderColor
params.description: Left border color of the event.

params.name: customStyle
params.description: Custom style of the event. The key of CSS property should be camelCase (e.g. {'fontSize': '12px'})

params.name: raw
params.description: Raw data of the event. it's an arbitrary property for anything.
